org.apache.jcs.auxiliary.disk
Class PurgatoryElement

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.jcs.auxiliary.disk.PurgatoryElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, ICacheElement
public class PurgatoryElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICacheElement, java.io.Serializable

Wrapper for cache elements in purgatory.

Elements are stored in purgatory when they are spooled to the auxilliary cache, but have not yet been written to disk.
